::Oblitertron::

Oblitertron ducked under Koj, growling as the ice beam hits his shoulder. He 
laughs as he sees Treadshot open fire on Koj, yelling as the blade goes into 
his shoulder, a shake from the huge bot dislodging it.

He takes a few steps back, firing at Koj, his shoulder leaking fuel.
